72
00:07:15,370 --> 00:07:17,060
How's that?

73
00:07:25,340 --> 00:07:30,920
♫  Snow has not stopped, flame is still burning  ♫

74
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:33,080
I boosted your cultivation,

75
00:07:34,420 --> 00:07:36,580
and you used it for this?

76
00:07:37,130 --> 00:07:40,020
Doesn't this make you happy? So why not?

77
00:07:40,020 --> 00:07:43,160
♫  Nobody can reach yet nobody listens  ♫

78
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:47,040
♫  Thousands of stars in your eyes  ♫

79
