427
00:38:26,180 --> 00:38:28,730
What are you waiting? Altogether, kill him!

428
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:50,840
How can this be?

429
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:52,360
The new moon hasn't affected you

430
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:54,360
