You're wrong.

434
00:39:14,710 --> 00:39:16,840
I am badly hurt.

435
00:39:16,840 --> 00:39:19,510
Today is truly my weakest day.

436
00:39:19,510 --> 00:39:24,630
If you want to kill me, this is indeed a golden chance.

437
00:39:25,700 --> 00:39:27,420
However...

