443
00:40:15,280 --> 00:40:17,370
Liao Tingyan.

444
00:40:20,030 --> 00:40:22,260
I'm badly hurt right now.

445
00:40:22,260 --> 00:40:27,050
This is a good chance for you.

446
00:40:35,450 --> 00:40:37,230
Got it!

447
00:40:46,510 --> 00:40:49,440
