00:41:00,530 --> 00:41:02,660
Sima Jiao can't fight back anymore.

451
00:41:02,660 --> 00:41:04,780
Take the sword and kill him!

452
00:41:04,780 --> 00:41:06,400
I don't kill people.

453
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:08,820
If he lives, you die!

454
00:41:08,820 --> 00:41:11,180
And more will die later!

455
00:41:11,180 --> 00:41:13,360
Hurry, do it!

456
00:41:13,360 --> 00:41:15,600
He's right.

